  "title": "Inside Sales Executive #77822",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/ Intralogistics Solutions</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Inside Sales Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Joo Koon</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Monday – Friday (8.30am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Commission + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Actively looking out and connect with potential clients, including initiating cold calls based on identified target segments.</li><li>Present and promote company products and services, generate new business opportunities, and handle quotations through the SAP C4C (CRM) system.</li><li>Achieve set sales objectives while maintaining profitability and supporting timely collection of account receivables.</li><li>Follow established internal workflows and ensure all business data is accurately maintained for effective reporting and forecasting.</li><li>Support the achievement of team objectives and participate in various ad-hoc projects when required.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Business, Engineering, or a related discipline.</li><li>Minimum 2 years of relevant experience; preferably with industrial or equipment sales background.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal abilities, capable of engaging and persuading customers.</li><li>Experience with telemarketing or outbound phone sales is an added advantage.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77822 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
